\pard\sa220 The first serious ablation set should include generic_sheet_col, generic_sheet_row, depth, sheet_mlp, sheet_qkv, sheet_attn_dmodel, sheet_attn_local, sheet_full_dmodel, and sheet_full_local. The other combinations are useful diagnostics, but they are not all equally high-conviction.\par
